| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0384 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2ea4740c-3e7a-5ac2-9273-e3b0d12fa15e"
